<br>
Left corpse at shady for rez, ported up with wizard and a paladin (in case we got a mob at zone-in).<br>
<br>
Two mobs immediately started pummeling wizard for around 200 a hit, and then paladin. I barely had enough time to hit hide and sneak before both dropped. Cleric in EC leaves, and I now have no escape route. I eventually get moved over by a sowed lich; it was moving so fast with sow that I couldn't get out of it's way fast enough.<br>
<br>
We get two groups together, figuring it will be enough to take out a measily two mobs and grab two corpses, and I figure I can slip out and grab my corpse. About 10 mobs aggro. Ten people die - everyone except me and a mage that was invised and never took it off. Mage gates successfully. I get rezzed down by guild leader, a cleric, with 11 seconds left until timer runs out.<br>
<br>
Two hours later, we get an uber guild to save us. (BIG thank you to The First Seal) We all get rezzed, and ported back down.<br>
<br>
Okay, so how do I get up there without getting wizard killed and starting this all over again? <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugeredshadowblade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gered Shadowblade</A> at: 3/30/02 2:24:23 am<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showPrevMessage?topicID=13809.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showNextMessage?topicID=13809.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13809.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.emailToFriend?topicID=13809.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.threadControl?topicID=13809.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=13809.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=13809.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding